name: PGL Arlington Major 2022
description:
The time has come when, after more than five years, another DOTA 2 major will be held in North America. PGL DOTA 2 MAJOR ARLINGTON will take place between August 4 and 14. The final three days of competition (August 12-14) will take place in front of an audience at Esports Stadium Arlington, North America's largest eSports venue. 
The top 18 teams in the world will converge on Arlington to battle it out for a prize pool of $500,000 and decisive points towards the most important DOTA 2 tournament of the season - The International.
